/* ==UserStyle==
@name           YouTube Tweaks
@namespace      userstyles.world/user/Pedro
@version        2025.12.5
@description    Hide Shorts, hide watched videos, change the number of videos per row & more!
@author         Pedro <pedro.sou@icloud.com>
@license        MIT
@preprocessor   stylus

